data.description: **CONTINGENT - Accepting Backup Offers** Nestled in one of the most highly sought-after areas of Neptune Beach - this one of a kind gem won't last long! Experience true coastal living by residing within biking (or golf cart!) distance to both the Atlantic Ocean and the Intercoastal Waterway, as well as Jarboe Park, Beaches Town Center, and other local shops and restaurants. This meticulously maintained brick home sits on a large, corner lot with mature oaks and offers ample space to enjoy the outdoors with a fenced in backyard and paver patio. Inside you will find multiple living spaces, three bedrooms, and a flex room that would make for the perfect home office, homework space, or workout room. The large master suite features its own wood-burning fireplace, dual walk-in closets, and a double vanity. Plenty of storage can be found in the oversized shed or two-car garage.  Updates include a brand new roof (2024), newer appliances (2020-2023), interior and exterior paint (2020-2021), paver patio (2021), and sprinkler system upgrades (2023). Homes like this do not come on the market very often - don't miss this opportunity!
